<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="es"><head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>¡Página no encontrada! | Propiedades en Chiapas</title>

  <link href="../css/css2_2.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f0f3f9 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      color: #1b2e84;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .illustration {
      width: 280px;
      max-width: 80%;
      animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes float {
      0%,100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 58px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin: 20px 0 10px;
      color: #1b2e84;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #374151;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 35px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .btn-home {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #1b2e84;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 36px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(27,46,132,0.3);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn-home:hover {
      background-color: #243d96;
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(27,46,132,0.4);
    }
    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      h1 { font-size: 42px; }
      p { font-size: 16px; padding: 0 20px; }
      .btn-home { font-size: 16px; padding: 12px 26px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- ILUSTRACIÓN -->
  <svg class="illustration" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
    <path fill="#1b2e84" d="M256 48C141.12 48 48 141.12 48 256s93.12 208 208 208 208-93.12 208-208S370.88 48 256 48zm0 384a176 176 0 1 1 0-352 176 176 0 0 1 0 352z"></path>
    <circle fill="#1b2e84" cx="184" cy="216" r="24"></circle>
    <circle fill="#1b2e84" cx="328" cy="216" r="24"></circle>
    <path fill="#1b2e84" d="M256 304c-44.18 0-80 27.34-80 61.09 0 8.84 7.16 16 16 16h128c8.84 0 16-7.16 16-16 0-33.75-35.82-61.09-80-61.09z"></path>
  </svg>

  <!-- TEXTO PRINCIPAL -->
  <h1>¡Ooops!</h1>
  <p>La página que buscas no existe o fue movida.<br>
  Pero no te preocupes, tenemos muchas propiedades esperándote.</p>

  <!-- BOTÓN -->
  <a href="https://propiedadesenchiapas.com" class="btn-home">Volver al inicio</a>

  <!-- PIE -->
  <div class="footer">© 2026 Propiedades en Chiapas</div>



</body></html>